246
00:10:47,240 --> 00:10:49,240
Puc passar?

247
00:10:49,240 --> 00:10:51,240
Puc passar, gos?

248
00:10:51,240 --> 00:10:53,240
O què? O no em deixes?

249
00:10:55,240 --> 00:10:57,240
Ara el tio

250
00:10:57,240 --> 00:10:59,240
s'ha ficat vergonyós.

251
00:10:59,240 --> 00:11:01,240
Ara dona la volta.

252
00:11:01,240 --> 00:11:03,240
S'ha ficat vergonyós.

253
00:11:03,240 --> 00:11:05,240
Mira que m'està abordant, eh?

254
00:11:05,240 --> 00:11:07,240
Doncs no m'ha donat l'oportunitat

255
00:11:07,240 --> 00:11:09,240
