256
00:11:25,240 --> 00:11:27,240
Aquest últim tram

257
00:11:27,240 --> 00:11:29,240
és completament

258
00:11:29,240 --> 00:11:31,240
salvati,

259
00:11:31,240 --> 00:11:33,240
que estic avançant molt lent.

260
00:11:33,240 --> 00:11:35,240
Mira, ara encara,

261
00:11:35,240 --> 00:11:37,240
