293
00:12:45,240 --> 00:12:47,240
però no està sembrat ni res.

294
00:12:47,240 --> 00:12:49,240
Veig una magnífica

295
00:12:49,240 --> 00:12:51,240
semiposta de sol i veig el llac, tu,

296
00:12:51,240 --> 00:12:53,240
