302
00:13:03,240 --> 00:13:05,240
però mireu, eh?, mireu, mireu.

303
00:13:05,240 --> 00:13:07,240
Ho, ho, ho!

304
00:13:07,240 --> 00:13:09,240
Brutal!

305
00:13:09,240 --> 00:13:11,240
Brutals vistes, tu.

306
00:13:11,240 --> 00:13:13,240
De tot, eh?

307
00:13:13,240 --> 00:13:15,240
De les muntanyes, de la plana,

308
00:13:15,240 --> 00:13:17,240
