315
00:13:29,240 --> 00:13:31,240
No puc anar per l'autopista com havia anat.

316
00:13:31,240 --> 00:13:33,240
L'haurem de superar. Hi ha un túnel, llavors

317
00:13:33,240 --> 00:13:35,240
