318
00:13:35,240 --> 00:13:37,240
I ja està.

319
00:13:37,240 --> 00:13:39,240
Sento un gos, com sempre.

320
00:13:39,240 --> 00:13:41,240
Vaig a plantar.

321
00:13:41,240 --> 00:13:43,240
Resum.

322
00:13:43,240 --> 00:13:45,240
18 km i 300 i pico

323
00:13:45,240 --> 00:13:47,240
de desnivell positiu.

324
00:13:47,240 --> 00:13:49,240
Cafès, un.

325
00:13:49,240 --> 00:13:51,240
Refrescos, dos.

326
00:13:51,240 --> 00:13:53,240
He parlat amb dues persones.

327
00:13:53,240 --> 00:13:55,240
El de la tenda de caça

328
00:13:55,240 --> 00:13:57,240
i el del hòstel.

329
00:13:57,240 --> 00:13:59,240
Incidents amb gossos, diríem que un.

330
00:13:59,240 --> 00:14:01,240
Avui, encara que podria dir mig.

331
00:14:01,240 --> 00:14:03,240
Realment no ha sigut un incident.

332
00:14:03,240 --> 00:14:05,240
I de diners

333
00:14:05,240 --> 00:14:07,240
tenim

334
00:14:07,240 --> 00:14:09,240
9 euros al supermercat,

335
00:14:09,240 --> 00:14:11,240
11 euros al dinar,

336
00:14:11,240 --> 00:14:13,240
40 euros de l'aparato aquest,

337
00:14:13,240 --> 00:14:15,240
2,20

338
00:14:15,240 --> 00:14:17,240
