339
00:14:17,240 --> 00:14:19,240
i 15 euros de la targeta SIM.

340
00:14:19,240 --> 00:14:21,240
Déu n'hi do, avui.

341
00:14:21,240 --> 00:14:23,240
Bueno, mireu, al final

342
00:14:23,240 --> 00:14:25,240
