364
00:15:07,240 --> 00:15:09,240
40, 40 i piu quilòmetres fins a Metzobo.

365
00:15:09,240 --> 00:15:11,240
Mil i pico de desnivell.

366
00:15:11,240 --> 00:15:13,240
Serà un etapón. Demà

367
00:15:13,240 --> 00:15:15,240
