383
00:15:45,240 --> 00:15:47,240
perquè és que el forat deu ser tan petit

384
00:15:47,240 --> 00:15:49,240
que

385
00:15:49,240 --> 00:15:51,240
és difícil

386
00:15:51,240 --> 00:15:53,240
