387
00:15:53,240 --> 00:15:55,240
Bueno, doncs

388
00:15:55,240 --> 00:15:57,240
intentaré seguir descobrint on està.

389
00:15:57,240 --> 00:15:59,240
Bueno,

390
00:15:59,240 --> 00:16:01,240
intentaré seguir-ho descobrint i

391
00:16:01,240 --> 00:16:03,240
si no ho descobreixo me n'hauré de comprar un altre

392
00:16:03,240 --> 00:16:05,240
i aquest l'enviaria a casa perquè algú

393
00:16:05,240 --> 00:16:07,240
